list.title: 2018 Aphrodite Games
list.description_title: The qualifiers for the 2018 Aphrodite Games will run between 5th June and 29th June 2018 with 4 qualifying workouts to be completed.
list.description: This year we look to build on from the previous years in establishing the Aphrodite Games as one of the most competitive and fun events in the region, and are delighted that you made the decision to take part in the competition. We are looking forward to having you be a part of the AG.

events.title: Qualifier 1
events.description:
15 calorie Row
6m One-Arm Dumbbell Overhead Lunges
30 Dumbbell Snatch - alternating
6m One-Arm Dumbbell Overhead Lunges

events.title: Qualifier 2
events.description:
60 Double Unders
15 Box Jump Overs
15 Chest to Bar
60 Double Unders
15 Box Jump Overs
15 Bar Muscle Ups

events.title: CLEAN LADDER E2MOM
events.description:
Every 2 minutes: 3 Cleans
0-2min: 80kg/45kg
2-4min: 90kg/55kg
etc. adding +10kg every 2min until failure to complete 3 repetitions within the given timeframe

events.title: Qualifier 4
events.description:
8 MIN AMRAP:
20 Thrusters
30 Bar Facing Burpees
40 Toes to Bar

Men - All Divisions: 55kg
Women - All Divisions: 35kg

list.title: NEW THE DUBAI FITNESS CHAMPIONSHIP
list.description: Created in 2012 to raise awareness on the importance of exercise and health, DFC has quickly gained momentum in the fitness world. Becoming an international fitness competition, attracting elite athletes from all over the world, awarding generous cash prizes and using Dubai as its host city has facilitated in DFC'92s rapid success. The Dubai Fitness Championship will continue to provide an exciting and challenging event for both participating athletes and spectators. In 2017, DFC promises to build on the success of the previous years by continue to attract the world'92s best, as well as upping the scale across all levels.
